'''膨脹地球說'''是一個[[假設|假設]]地球上的大陆漂移都是因地球膨脹所致的學說。相反，{{link-en|地球物理全球降溫|Geophysical global cooling|收縮地球說}}則是假設地球上的[[板塊|板塊]]移動都是因地球收縮所致的學說。<ref>[http://www.bbm.me.uk/portsdown/PH_061_History_a.htm The History of Continental Drift - Before Wegener<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051123101326/http://www.bbm.me.uk/portsdown/PH_061_History_a.htm |date=2005-11-23 }}</ref>自從[[板塊構造論|板塊構造論]]出現後，膨脹地球說和收縮地球說便被科學界一致否定了。

==不同形式的膨脹地球說==
膨脹地球主要有3種形式：
# 地球的質量一直保持不變，重力隨著時間推移下降。
# 地球的質量一直增加，重力保持不變。
# 地球的質量和重力一直增加。

===質量不變說===
1834年，在貝格爾號第二次遠航期間，[[查尔斯·达尔文|查尔斯·达尔文]]調查了[[巴塔哥尼亞|巴塔哥尼亞]]的階梯狀平原，並發現南美洲一巨大區域的海拔正在不斷上升。當他的導師[[查爾斯·萊爾|查爾斯·萊爾]]指出這可能是因地殼的作用力所致時，达尔文卻假設令這個區域海拔上升是因「地球的体积正在增加」。於1835年，他擴充了這個假設，並指出[[安地斯山脈|安地斯山脈]]是地球曲線膨脹所形成的山脈。不久，他又指出當山脈增高，海床就會加深，並因此解釋了[[珊瑚礁|珊瑚礁]]的結構與分佈。<ref>{{Citation | last =Herbert | first =Sandra | publication-date =1991 | title =Charles Darwin as a prospective geological author | periodical =British Journal for the History of Science | volume =24 | issue =2 | pages =159–192 [184–188] | url =http://darwin-online.org.uk/content/frameset?viewtype=text&itemID=A342&pageseq=26 | accessdate =24 October 2008 | doi =10.1017/S0007087400027060 | jstor =4027165 | archive-date =2012-10-21 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20121021033901/http://darwin-online.org.uk/content/frameset?viewtype=text&itemID=A342&pageseq=26 | dead-url =no }}, pp. [http://darwin-online.org.uk/content/frameset?pageseq=20&itemID=A342&viewtype=text 178] {{Wayback|url=http://darwin-online.org.uk/content/frameset?pageseq=20&itemID=A342&viewtype=text |date=20131004220224 }}, [http://darwin-online.org.uk/content/frameset?viewtype=text&itemID=A342&pageseq=26 184] {{Wayback|url=http://darwin-online.org.uk/content/frameset?viewtype=text&itemID=A342&pageseq=26 |date=20121021033901 }}, [http://darwin-online.org.uk/content/frameset?pageseq=31&itemID=A342&viewtype=text 189] {{Wayback|url=http://darwin-online.org.uk/content/frameset?pageseq=31&itemID=A342&viewtype=text |date=20131004220519 }}, also Darwin, C. R. Geological diary: Elevation of Patagonia. (5.1834) CUL-DAR34.40-60 Transcribed by Kees Rookmaaker (Darwin Online), pp. [http://darwin-online.org.uk/content/frameset?pageseq=35&itemID=CUL-DAR34.40-60&viewtype=text 58–59] {{Wayback|url=http://darwin-online.org.uk/content/frameset?pageseq=35&itemID=CUL-DAR34.40-60&viewtype=text |date=20131004220357 }}.</ref>

1889年和1909年，{{link-en|羅伯托·曼托瓦尼|Roberto Mantovani}}發表了關於膨脹地球和大陸漂移的假說。他假設在地球較小的時候，整個表面都是由大陸覆蓋。[[热胀冷缩|热胀冷缩]]導致[[火山活動|火山活動]]，並將一個大陸拆分成幾個大陸，而大陸之間的空隙便成為了海洋。<ref>{{Citation | author=Mantovani, R.| author-link =| title = Les fractures de l’écorce terrestre et la théorie de Laplace | journal=Bull. Soc. Sc. Et Arts Réunion | pages=41–53| year=1889}}</ref><ref>{{Citation | author=Mantovani, R.| title = L’Antarctide |journal=Je m’instruis. La science pour tous |volume=38 | pages=595–597| year=1909}}</ref>雖然[[阿尔弗雷德·魏格纳|阿尔弗雷德·魏格纳]]發現曼托瓦尼的假說和其[[大陸漂移說|大陸漂移說]]相近，但大陸漂移說並沒有指出膨脹地球是大陸漂移的原因。<ref>{{Citation | author=Wegener, A. | title = The Origin of Continents and Oceans | year=1929/1966 |publisher=Courier Dover Publications|isbn=0-486-61708-4}} See [[:s:de:Die_Entstehung_der_Kontinente_und_Ozeane|Online version]] in German.</ref>

而[[約翰·喬利|約翰·喬利]]的假說則介乎於膨脹地球說和收縮地球說之間。他的學說指出地球正在膨脹，但在膨脹期間會失去熱力，致使岩漿凝固。之後，地球便會因缺乏熱力而收縮。<ref>{{Citation | author=Hohl, R.| title = Geotektonische Hypothesen | journal=Die Entwicklungsgeschichte der Erde. Brockhaus Nachschlagewerk Geologie mit einem ABC der Geologie |edition=4. |volume=Bd. 1 | pages=279–321 | year =1970}}</ref>

===質量增加說===
於1888年，[[伊凡·亚尔科夫斯基|伊凡·亚尔科夫斯基]]假說[[以太|以太]]被地球吸收，並被轉化為新的化學元素，致使地球質量和容量增加。這符合了亚尔科夫斯基的力學解釋萬有引力說。<ref>{{Citation | author=Yarkovsky, Ivan Osipovich| title = Hypothese cinetique de la Gravitation universelle et connexion avec la formation des elements chimiques | place= Moskau | year=1888}}</ref>而{{link-de|奧特·克里斯托弗·希爾根貝格|Ott Christoph Hilgenberg}}於1933年和1974年<ref name="Hilgenberg.1933">{{Citation | author=Hilgenberg, O.C. | title = Vom wachsenden Erdball (The Expanding Earth) | bibcode=1933QB981.H6....... | place=Berlin | publisher=Giessmann & Bartsch | year=1933}}</ref><ref name="Hilgenberg.1974">{{Citation | author=Hilgenberg, O.C. | title = Geotektonik, neuartig gesehen | journal=Geotektonische Forschungen| volume=45|pages=1–194 | year=1974 | isbn= 978-3-510-50011-6}}</ref>，以及[[尼古拉·特斯拉|尼古拉·特斯拉]]於1935年<ref>{{Citation | author=Tesla, N. | title=Expanding Sun Will Explode Someday Tesla Predicts | place=New York | publisher=New York Herald Tribune | year=1935 | url=http://en.wikisource.org/wiki/The_New_York_Herald_Tribune/1935/08/18/Expanding_Sun_Will_Explode_Some_Day_Tesla_Predicts | accessdate=2013-10-04 | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112030358/https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/The_New_York_Herald_Tribune/1935/08/18/Expanding_Sun_Will_Explode_Some_Day_Tesla_Predicts | dead-url=no }}</ref>的質量增加假說都與以太有關。

在初步上支持大陸漂移後，晚期澳大利亞地質學家{{link-en|塞繆爾·沃倫·凱里|Samuel Warren Carey}}自從20世紀50年代開始直到他的死亡，他都主張質量增加說。<ref name="japantimes1">{{Citation | author=Jeff Ogrisseg | url=http://search.japantimes.co.jp/cgi-bin/fl20091122x2.html | title=Dogmas may blinker mainstream scientific thinking | year=2009 | work=The Japan Times | accessdate=2013-10-04 | archive-date=2012-05-24 | archive-url=https://archive.is/20120524182232/http://www.japantimes.co.jp/text/fl20091122x2.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>他亦指出[[隱沒帶|隱沒帶]]在[[海底扩张学说|海底扩张学说]]中與[[中洋脊|中洋脊]]相違。<ref>S. W. Carey, The Expanding Earth – An essay review, 1975, Earth Science Reviews, vol. 11-2, pp.105-143, {{DOI|10.1016/0012-8252(75)90097-5}}</ref>從1956年開始，他便開始主張質量增加說，並認為膨脹地球說與[[宇宙學|宇宙學]]的[[膨胀宇宙的未来|膨胀宇宙]]有關。<ref>{{citation |title= Theories of the earth and universe: a history of dogma in the earth sciences |author= Samuel Warren Carey |edition= illustrated |publisher= Stanford University Press |year= 1988 |isbn= 978-0-8047-1364-1 |pages= 347–350 |url= http://books.google.es/books?id=l_0l0KOdHLoC&pg=PA347&lpg=PA347&dq=sam+elton&source=bl&ots=GaxCPuvbKl&sig=uQCezu2rHiSzTeMy6Y1TuiSoR6w&hl=en&ei=x2ToTvTvJMnJhAev_cHcCg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=sam%20elton&f=false |accessdate= 2013-10-04 |archive-date= 2018-10-06 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181006081326/https://books.google.es/books?id=l_0l0KOdHLoC&pg=PA347&lpg=PA347&dq=sam+elton&source=bl&ots=GaxCPuvbKl&sig=uQCezu2rHiSzTeMy6Y1TuiSoR6w&hl=en&ei=x2ToTvTvJMnJhAev_cHcCg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=sam%20elton&f=false |dead-url= no }}</ref>

{{link-en|布魯斯·希森|Bruce C. Heezen}}則支持凱里的質量增加說，但後來卻表示不再支持。<ref>Oreskes, Naomi, 2003, ''Plate Tectonics: An Insider's History Of The Modern Theory Of The Earth'', Westview Press, p. 23, ISBN 0813341329</ref><ref>Frankel, Henry, ''The Continental Drift Debate,'' Ch. 7 in ''Scientific controversies'', p. 226, 1987, Cambridge University Press, ISBN 978-0-521-27560-6</ref>儘管不少科學家均表示不再支持凱里的質量增加說，但不少支持膨脹地球說的科學家仍然支持凱里，其中包括澳大利亞地質學家詹姆斯·馬克斯盧。<ref name="japantimes1" />

漫畫家尼爾·亞當斯亦支持膨脹地球說，並且自己也發展了一個假說。該假說指出[[正電子|正電子]]在地球內出現，與其他粒子結合，並釋放[[伽马射线|伽马射线]]。亞當斯亦指出這種反應會產生新特質。<ref name=wired2001>{{Citation | last=O'Brien | first=Jeffrey | url=http://www.wired.com/wired/archive/9.03/adams_pr.html | title=Master of the Universe | journal=Wired | issue=9.03 | accessdate=2 June 2008 | date=March 2001 | archive-date=2013-09-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921135242/http://www.wired.com/wired/archive/9.03/adams_pr.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=novella2009>{{cite web |title= No Growing Earth, But a Growing Problem With Science Journalism |author= Steven Novella |publisher= skepticblog.org |date= 2009-11-03 |url= http://www.skepticblog.org/2009/11/23/no-growing-earth-but-a-growing-problem-with-science-journalism/ |accessdate= 2013-10-04 |archive-date= 2011-11-01 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20111101133619/http://www.skepticblog.org/2009/11/23/no-growing-earth-but-a-growing-problem-with-science-journalism/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>

===重力增加說===
[[保羅·狄拉克|保羅·狄拉克]]於1938年假說[[万有引力常数|万有引力常数]]在數十億年以來一直在下降。之後，德國物理學家[[帕斯库尔·约当|帕斯库尔·约当]]於1964年假說所有行星都在慢慢膨脹。但是，在膨脹地球說被否定前，大部份科學家都不支持重力增加說。<ref>{{Citation | author=Jordan, P. | title = The expanding earth: some consequences of Dirac's gravitation hypothesis | place=Oxford | publisher=Pergamon Press | year=1971}}</ref><ref>{{Citation | author=Born, M. | title = Die Relativitätstheorie Einsteins (Einstein's theory of relativity)| place=Berlin-Heidelberg-New York | publisher=Springer-publisher | year =1964/2003 |isbn=3-540-00470-X}}</ref>

==科學界共識==

膨脹地球說從來沒有成為一個合理和可被証实的學說。<ref name="japantimes1" />在20世紀60年代，[[板塊構造論|板塊構造論]]的出現令膨脹地球說被科學界一致否定，因為板塊構造論更符合地球科學，並且更能解釋板塊的移動。<ref name="japantimes1" />

以下為科學界找出的反對膨脹地球說和支持板塊構造論的證據：
*透過現代先進的[[大地测量学|大地测量学]]技術和模型，科學家們發現地球並非在膨脹，即地球的半徑每年並沒有增加0.2毫米。<ref name=Wu>{{Cite journal
| doi = 10.1029/2011GL047450
| volume = 38
| pages = 5 PP.
| last = Wu
| first = X.
| coauthors = X. Collilieux, Z. Altamimi, B. L. A. Vermeersen, R. S. Gross, I. Fukumori
| title = Accuracy of the International Terrestrial Reference Frame origin and Earth expansion
| journal = Geophysical Research Letters
| accessdate = 17 July 2011
| date = 8 July 2011
| url = http://www.agu.org/pubs/crossref/2011/2011GL047450.shtml
| bibcode = 2011GeoRL..3813304W
| archive-date = 2012-10-03
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121003151356/http://www.agu.org/pubs/crossref/2011/2011GL047450.shtml
| dead-url = yes
}}</ref>領導科學家指出「我們獨立的研究確認了固體地球目前並不會變得越來越大」。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2011/08/110817120527.htm |title=''It's a Small World, After All: Earth Is Not Expanding, NASA Research Confirms,'' ScienceDaily (Aug. 17, 2011) |access-date=2013-10-04 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112042330/http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2011/08/110817120527.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 
*透過地質學家，大地測量學家和地球物理學家的測量，現代板塊的移動和俯衝帶的變化並非如膨脹地球說所述，因地球膨脹所致。<ref>Fowler (1990), pp 281 & 320–327; Duff (1993), pp 609–613; Stanley (1999), pp 223–226</ref><ref name="Bucher2005">{{Citation|doi=10.2138/am.2005.1718|title=Blueschists, eclogites, and decompression assemblages of the Zermatt-Saas ophiolite: High-pressure metamorphism of subducted Tethys lithosphere|year=2005|last1=Bucher|first1=K.|journal=American Mineralogist|volume=90|pages=821}}</ref><ref name="VanDerLee1997">{{Citation|doi=10.1038/386266a0|title=Seismic image of the subducted trailing fragments of the Farallon plate|year=1997|last1=Van Der Lee|first1=Suzan|last2=Nolet|first2=Guust|journal=Nature|volume=386|pages=266|issue=6622|bibcode = 1997Natur.386..266V }}</ref>
*透過岩石碎片成像，地幔是支撐著地表的，而膨脹地球將令到地幔無法支撐地表。<ref name="Bucher2005"/><ref name="VanDerLee1997"/> 
*[[古地磁學|古地磁學家]]發現4億年前地球的半徑是現代地球半徑的102 ± 2.8%。<ref name=mcelhinney>{{Citation | author=McElhinney, M. W., Taylor, S. R., and Stevenson, D. J. | title = Limits to the expansion of Earth, Moon, Mars, and Mercury and to changes in the gravitational constant | year = 1978 | journal=Nature | volume=271 | pages=316–321 | doi=10.1038/271316a0 | issue=5643|bibcode = 1978Natur.271..316M }}</ref><ref>Schmidt, P. W. and Clark, D. A. (1980), ''The response of palaeomagnetic data to Earth expansion'', Geophysical Journal of the Royal Astronomical Society, 61: 95–100, 1980, {{doi|10.1111/j.1365-246X.1980.tb04306.x}}</ref>然而，古地磁學家所採用的數據收集方法被俄羅斯地質學家俞·丘季諾夫批評。<ref>Yu Chudinov, Eduction concept of the earth's expansion theory: main grounds, VSP, Utrecht, 2001, ISBN 90-6764-299-1</ref>
*透過檢測地球的[[轉動慣量|轉動慣量]]，科學家們發現地球在近6.2億年內沒有明顯的體積變化。<ref name=williams>{{Citation | author=Williams, G.E. | title=Geological constraints on the Precambrian history of Earth’s rotation and the moon’s orbit | url=http://www.eos.ubc.ca/~mjelline/453website/eosc453/E_prints/1999RG900016.pdf | format=PDF | year=2000 | journal=Reviews of Geophysics | volume=38 | number=1 | pages=37–59 | doi=10.1029/1999RG900016 | bibcode=2000RvGeo..38...37W | accessdate=2013-10-04 | archive-date=2015-12-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151224032245/http://www.eos.ubc.ca/~mjelline/453website/eosc453/E_prints/1999RG900016.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>

